# .claude Naming Guide

Core principle:

- path decides scope
- file name decides topic
- prefix decides status

Recommended examples:

- `.claude/skills/loloop/`
- `.claude/plans/loloop/active-site-loop-plan-v1.md`
- `.claude/plans/loloop/evolution-2026-04-10-bootstrap.md`
- `.claude/logs/loloop/2026-04-10-run-01.log`

Avoid:

- `myplan.md`
- `local-loop.md`
- deeply nesting project runtime data inside skill folders

